- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper introduces a new approach for object instance mining. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image analysis and object detection. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves information propagation on spatial and appearance graphs.
